name: The Husky Pack Gold VIP Pass

metadata.description:
The Husky Pack is a mission driven NFT project that looks to merge Web2 with Web3! 
As a Husky Pack VIP Pass Holder, you get to experience the bridge between the blockchain and ecommerce. You will have access to a unique Web3 shopping experience on our website and be rewarded with up to 30% discounts on all purchases. 
Join The Pack! Learn more about The Husky Pack!
